      "id": "note--9ad0e1f2-a3b4-4c5d-6e7f-9a0b1c2d3e4f",
      "created": "2026-04-03T02:15:00.000Z",
      "modified": "2026-04-03T02:15:00.000Z",
      "abstract": "Novel findings in this investigation",
      "content": "1. defence-np.net is a previously unreported SideWinder C2 domain not found in any prior public reporting. 2. Azerbaijan-Russia diplomatic targeting represents a new geographic and thematic expansion for SideWinder beyond South Asia. 3. OPSEC failure: typo subdomain 'dialomatic' reveals rushed infrastructure deployment. 4. Spaceship Inc is a new registrar in SideWinder's arsenal (historically Hostinger/Namecheap). 5. AWS hosting behind Cloudflare is atypical for SideWinder (historically HZ Hosting/BlueVPS/GhostNET).",
      "object_refs": ["campaign--f4a5b6c7-d8e9-4f0a-1b2c-3d4e5f6a7b8c"]
    }
